  "title": "MultiBeds",
  "description": "::Design Your Bed:: Pick the style, block texture, blanket pattern and color (or use a banner). Dye your sheets and pillow case. Choose an embroidery or create/use/share a custom one.",
  "body": "<center>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JyytxgF6/images/355f241db2c195979242b7a5b99623f04ee7c1e5.png\" width=\"840\" height=\"105\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JyytxgF6/images/befc2435a7342a6ccddb769f442d64f835d15618.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"115\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">***&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/shetiphiancore\" rel=\"nofollow\">ShetiPhianCore</a> Required! ***</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Make the bed of your dreams. Choose patterns, textures, and colors. Even draw your own pixel art on top!</p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>: <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/multibeds/pages/current\" rel=\"nofollow\">Item Recipes and Info</a> :</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JyytxgF6/images/948ec107d7d69b862765f1f49368ef0f32eb417f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"85\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JyytxgF6/images/4fab7bb587852012e38c6b169c39c095b42cb710.png\" width=\"850\" height=\"470\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JyytxgF6/images/948ec107d7d69b862765f1f49368ef0f32eb417f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"85\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RVS4GYo.gif\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Apply Sheets, pillow cover, blanket, and art to your bed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g9UJ3tZ.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Make your own pixel art in-game.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ASfK1zp.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Multiple styles of bed to choose from. Add any block to change appearance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j6DYvno.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Click a blanket onto a loom to customize the color/pattern.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FTN3gDm.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Beds automatically join in wide/bunk configurations.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MWS5OpX.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Custom ladders to fit your bunk bed.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JyytxgF6/images/948ec107d7d69b862765f1f49368ef0f32eb417f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"85\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Submit localization files on <a href=\"https://github.com/ShetiPhian/Localizations-and-Issues\">github</a>.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Found a bug?, use the <a href=\"https://github.com/ShetiPhian/Localizations-and-Issues/issues\">Issue Tracker</a>.</strong></p>\n</center>",
